title: Gundam Unicorn Complete 1 - 7 (1 - 1.5GB Episodes / 1080p)
description:
Gundam Unicorn All Episodes (1 - 7)

Encoded personally by me (Jipzy)

Video Resolution - 1920x1080 (All Episodes)

Audio Bit Rate varies per episode as it's HE-AAC 128kbps on some and LC-AAC 192kbps on others (128 didn't want to work for all episodes :/

Episodes range from just under 1GB to just over 1.6GB's for the final episode seeing how it's an hour and a half

Episodes are fully in English (No Jap Audio or Subs, but by request I can upload those for those who might want them)

My Upload speed isn't the greatest (Just over 220kbps) so bare with me :/

Most Importantly ENJOY! I know I did!


Episodes in Order

Gundam Unicorn - 01 - Day of the Unicorn
Gundam Unicorn - 02 - The Second Coming of Char (The Red Comet)
Gundam Unicorn - 03 - The Ghost of Laplace
Gundam Unicorn - 04 - At The Bottom of the Gravity Well
Gundam Unicorn - 05 - Black Unicorn
Gundam Unicorn - 06 - Two Worlds, Two Tomorrows (The Sky and the Stars)
Gundam Unicorn - 07 - Over The Rainbow
